name: J Crew Collection Grommet Parlour Hobo in Black
description:
Barely used and in great condition. Purchased from J Crew for 298.00. Great size, tote handles and cross body adjustable strap. Here is the description from J Crew:

Part motorcycle chic, part impeccable uptown construction, it's one of our favorite shapes in soft pebbled leather and a tricked-out body with a smattering of studs and grommets. With multiple pockets to keep you organized and an adjustable strap for versatility. Top snap closure with two zip pockets. Shiny gold hardware. Interior front-wall split-patch cell pocket, back-wall zip pocket. Cotton twill lining. Part of the J.Crew Collection. Removable, adjustable shoulder strap fully extends to 22". 5" handle drop. 13 3/4"H x 15 3/4"W x 4 1/4"D
